creator: In A Day Development
descriptionHtml:
If you are a Sheep Breeder, HerdBoss will revolutionize the way you do business!

Keeping track of all the details about a flock of sheep can be a headache. That headache becomes a migraine when the flock grows and your operation expands.

HerdBoss for Sheep solves this problem!

A complete end-to-end solution, HerdBoss for Sheep tracks everything about your flock in a simple and intuitive way that will help you and your entire team save time and money, and increase accuracy and completeness of your tracking.

- Keeps track of all the details about each of your sheep, including name, scrapie tag, sex, DNA, and dozens of other pieces of information
- Tracks the breeders that you buy sheep from
- Tracks the buyers that you sell sheep to
- Keeps all of the weights of your sheep over time
- Lets you know which sheep have had what shots, and when
- Helps you track when your sheep have mated, and with whom
- Lets you know when you should expect new lambs to be born, and who the expectant dams are
- Displays the full lineage for any sheep in your flock, including Dams-and-Sires or just Sires based on your preference
- Generates a simple one-page or two-page report that contains all of the information about any sheep in your flock which makes it easy to tell buyers all about the animal
- Produce nearly a dozen reports about your herd, including the lambs that have been born, the production of your sires, the lambs which are expected, the rams, the ewes, the whole flock, and more!

All of this information is tied to your HerdBoss.com account, and is kept in-sync across all of your iPhones and iPads as well as at HerdBoss.com. Now you can have workers in the field entering medicine shot information or tracking mating information while you enter notes about the same animals, and have all of the data saved and shared for your whole team to see.

You can use HerdBoss without a 4G or WiFi connection! If you don't have signal out in the field, no problem! You can still enter in all of your information and when you get back into 4G or WiFi, HerdBoss will sync all of the new information with the cloud.
descriptionShort: If you are a Sheep Breeder, HerdBoss will revolutionize the way you do business!

title: HerdBoss

creator: In A Day Development
descriptionHtml:
Now supporting Sheep, Goats, Cattle, and Dogs!

If you need herd management, HerdBoss will revolutionize the way you do business!

Keeping track of all the details about your animals can be a headache. That headache becomes a migraine when your operation grows and expands.

HerdBoss solves this problem!

A complete end-to-end solution, HerdBoss tracks everything about your animals in a simple and intuitive way that will help you and your entire team save time and money, and increase accuracy and completeness of your tracking.

- Keeps track of all the details about each of your animals, including name, registration number, sex, DNA, and dozens of other pieces of information
- Track multiple species in one account
- Organize your animals into multiple groups
- Tracks the breeders that you buy animals from
- Tracks the buyers that you sell animals to
- Keeps all of the weights of your animals over time
- Lets you know which animals have had what shots, and when
- Helps you track when your animals have mated, and with whom
- Lets you know when you should expect new offspring to be born, and who the expectant dams are
- Displays the full lineage for any animal in your herd, including Dams-and-Sires or just Sires based on your preference
- Generates a simple one-page or two-page report that contains all of the information about any animal in your herd which makes it easy to tell buyers all about the animal
- Produce more than 20 reports about your herd, including the offspring that have been born, the production of your sires, the births which are expected soon, weight gain, medical treatments, and income produced by Sires and Dams!
- Bulk Actions available that make large updates easy
- Track Semen Straw inventory and history.

All of this information is tied to your HerdBoss.com account, and is kept in-sync across all of your iPhones and iPads as well as at HerdBoss.com. Now you can have workers in the field entering medicine shot information or tracking mating information while you enter notes about the same animals, and have all of the data saved and shared for your whole team to see.

You can use HerdBoss without a 5G or WiFi connection! If you don't have signal out in the field, no problem! You can still enter in all of your information and when you get back into 5G or WiFi, HerdBoss will sync all of the new information with the cloud.
descriptionShort: Goats. Cattle. Dogs. Sheep!

Added ability to track Semen Straw Inventory and Usage.
Lots of UI improvements.
